title: Joe Flacco: We'll see what's out there, don't want to sign with someone for the sake of it

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: Joe Flacco: We'll see what's out there, don't want to sign with someone for the sake of it
sources.description: Joe Flacco wrapped up his 18th season with his first trip to the Pro Bowl and the prospect of a 19th season came up during a Wednesday visit to PFT Live.
